* Put people in the driver’s seat 
* Master the basics 
* Work is part of life - not life 
* Develop your ppl as if they will be your boss
* Being yourself is your best approach

* The world is a circle - it all comes back
* It takes hours to forget what you said Days to forget what you did  But decades to forget how you made them feel
